    Click the link below list the Windfarms aggregated in the Windfarm 
    Service.  (Search criteria can be entered for either URL).
</p>
<div id="apilinks">
    <ul>
        <li>
            <a rel="windfarm" href="#" title="windfarm" data-input="searchcriteria">/api/windfarm</a>
